  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK427">
<l>aṟivuṭaiyā rāva taṟivā raṟivilā</l>
<l>raḵtaṟi kallā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise are those who know beforehand what will happen those who do not know this are the unwise.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
